🎵 Mood-Based Song Recommendation AI

This project is an AI-powered music recommendation system that suggests songs based on the user’s mood. The application uses Natural Language Processing (NLP) to analyze emotions and returns curated song recommendations.

It is built with:

Frontend: React.js (Vite)

Backend: Node.js + Express

AI / ML: TensorFlow.js / HuggingFace API (NLP)

Database: MongoDB (Atlas)

🚀 Features

✅ Detects mood from text input (e.g., “I am happy today”)
✅ Suggests songs matching the mood (happy, sad, energetic, relaxed, etc.)
✅ Clean & responsive frontend with React
✅ REST API backend with Express
✅ Songs stored and fetched from MongoDB
✅ Easy to extend with more moods and songs